<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA511_02_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema511_02_0003.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema511_02.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema511_02_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">학급 임원 선거를 하는 날에 서아네 반 여학생은 14명 중에서 2명이 결석했고 남학생은 10명 모두 출석했습니다. 출석한 학생이 모두 선거에 참여했다면 선거에 참여한 학생은 모두 몇 명인지 알아봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="flex align_start">
          <div class="picture_wrap">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 2034 1361" fill="none">
              <text fill="white" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-size="40" letter-spacing="-0.5px" lang="y">
                <tspan x="1216.11" y="297.545">학급 임원 선거</tspan>
                <tspan x="1231.91" y="345.545">&lt;참여 인원&gt;</tspan>
              </text>
              <text fill="white" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-size="40" letter-spacing="-0.5px" lang="y">
                <tspan x="1139" y="407.545">여학생: 14명 (결석: 2명)</tspan>
                <tspan x="1139" y="455.545">남학생: 10명</tspan>
              </text>
              <text fill="#222222" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-size="32" letter-spacing="-0.5px" lang="y">
                <tspan x="1263" y="547.636">투표함</tspan>
              </text>
              <text fill="#222222" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-size="32" letter-spacing="-0.5px" lang="y">
                <tspan x="948.266" y="1120.64">여학생 14명 중에서</tspan>
                <tspan x="970.594" y="1156.64">2명이 결석했어.</tspan>
              </text>
              <text fill="#222222" xml:space="preserve" style="white-space: pre" font-size="32" letter-spacing="-0.5px" lang="y">
                <tspan x="1359.25" y="1120.64">남학생은 10명이</tspan>
                <tspan x="1372.03" y="1156.64">모두 출석했어.</tspan>
              </text>
            </svg>
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA511_02_SU/0003_content.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
            <button class="zoom"></button>
          </div>

          <div class="input_area">
            <article class="page page_1">
              <h3 lang="y">선거에 참여한 여학생은 몇 명인지 식으로 나타내어 구해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="group_box">
                  <span>14-</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="12"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_2">
              <h3 lang="y">선거에 참여한 학생은 모두 몇 명인지 하나의 식으로 나타내어 구해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="group_box">
                  <span>14-</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer3">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <span>+</span>
                <div class="input_wrap answer4">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="10"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="input_wrap answer5">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="22"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
              <h3 lang="y">앞에서 나타낸 식을 계산하는 순서를 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <p>여학생 수를 먼저 구하고 남학생 수를 더하므로 앞에서부터 차례대로 계산합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
        <article class="page page_4">
          <div class="summarize_wrap">
            <div class="summarize">
              <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>
              <div class="row row1 gap_0">
                <span>14-2+10=</span>
                <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="1">12</button>
                <span>+10=</span>
                <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="2">22</button>
                
                <div class="hidden_obj" data-pair="1">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA511_02_SU/0003_obj1.svg" alt="연결선" />
                </div>
                <div class="hidden_obj" data-pair="2">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA511_02_SU/0003_obj2.svg" alt="연결선" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="row row2" lang="y">
                <span>덧셈과 뺄셈이 섞여 있는 식은</span>
                <button class="reveal_btn">앞에서부터</button>
                <span>차례대로 계산합니다.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
